{"id":646048,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/06/举报：鲁迅、梁启超、陈独秀、严复、郭沫若等人/","date":"2020-06-02T14:36:16Z","modified":"2020-06-02T22:35:00Z","title":"举报：鲁迅、梁启超、陈独秀、严复、郭沫若等人已违法","content":"<p>CDT编者按：北京市卫健委出台了一个“中医药条例”，用来保护中医的发展。其中有一条这样的内容：</p>\n<p>第五十四条 违反本条例第三十六条第二款之规定，诋毁、污蔑中医药，寻衅滋事，扰乱公共秩序，构成违反治安管理行为的，由公安机关依法给予治安管理处罚；构成犯罪的，依法追究刑事责任。</p>\n<p>于是网友举报已违法的一系列名人。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646049\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1039\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1.jpeg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-144x300.jpeg 144w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-493x1024.jpeg 493w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-768x1596.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-739x1536.jpeg 739w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/1-986x2048.jpeg 986w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646050\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1039\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2.jpeg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2-144x300.jpeg 144w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2-493x1024.jpeg 493w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2-768x1596.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2-739x1536.jpeg 739w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/2-986x2048.jpeg 986w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-646051\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1039\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/3.jpeg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/3-144x300.jpeg 144w, https://chinadigitaltimes.